{
  "id": "RAW_67e64e",
  "title": "HumanOmni：首个专注人类中心场景的多模态大模型，视觉与听觉融合的突破！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/cO6xEAOCRUsLmoiDbq12tw",
  "date": "2025-02-28 13:07:25",
  "author": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "siteName": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-bottom: 3px;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 5px 18px;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">01</span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-left: 18px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n       <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">模型介绍</span>\n      </section>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\">HumanOmni</span>是业内首个理解以人为中心的场景，可以同时处理视觉信息、音频信息的多模态大模型。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在人类中心场景中，理解和处理视觉与听觉信息至关重要。文章指出，当前方法大多关注于视觉-语言模型，但缺乏对音频输入的处理能力，导致对场景的理解不完整。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">近期一些可以同时处理视频+音频的模型被提出，但是由于缺乏大规模专门的人类中心数据集以及缺乏针对人物场景的针对性网络架构，导致其对于人物中心场景的理解能力还有较大的提升空间。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong>论文主要创新：</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></h3>\n  <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"126504\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 15px 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(84, 160, 247);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75;\">\n      <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n       <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;\">提出了HumanOmni，首个专注于人物中心场景理解的可以同时处理视觉+声音的多模态大语言模型。</p></li>\n       <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;\">构建了包含240万个人类中心视频片段的数据集，使用多个先进的模型进行联合校验，生成超过1400万条指令，以促进对多样化人类中心场景的理解。</p></li>\n       <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;\">人工对5w条视频片段进行标注，产生了超过10w条高质量指令，这些数据进一步提升了我们对于人物场景的理解能力。在情绪识别、面部描述、动作理解等多个人物相关的任务下，我们的HumanOmni均达到了sota的水平，同时我们实验验证了视觉+音频的联合输入相比单独使用视觉和单独使用音频的优势。</p></li>\n      </ul>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <section>\n   <section>\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section>\n       <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n        <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">模型架构</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017461\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/18cee154-e3ed-4571-15bc-34eb83320500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" title=\"\" width=\"1213\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/18cee154-e3ed-4571-15bc-34eb83320500/public\"></p>\n  <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"126504\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 15px 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(84, 160, 247);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75;\">\n      <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n       <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;\">在视觉理解部分，利用三个不同的分支来分别处理面部相关问题、人体相关问题、环境交互相关问题。设计一个指令驱动的融合模块来利用用户的输入指令生成不同的权重，从而将这三个分支的视觉特征进行自适应融合。</p></li>\n       <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;\">将视觉token、音频token、文本token结合后送入大语言模型，实现对于多模态信息的同步处理。</p></li>\n      </ul>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型下载链接：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://modelscope.cn/collections/HumanOmni-shipinrenwulijie-234cdc0e5fe247</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://huggingface.co/StarJiaxing/HumanOmni-7B</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">代码地址：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://github.com/HumanMLLM/HumanOmni</span><br></p>\n  <section>\n   <section>\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;\">\n       <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong>模型训练</strong></span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型训练分为三个阶段</span></strong></p>\n  <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"126504\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 15px 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(84, 160, 247);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong>第一阶段</strong>是视觉能力构建，在这一阶段，我们利用生成的指令数据以及人工标注的指令数据构建了模型的视觉能力，其中我们更新了三个分支的视觉映射器的参数、指令驱动的融合模块的参数以及大语言模型的参数。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第二阶段</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是听觉能力发展，在这一阶段，我们基于第一阶段的大语言模型的参数，利用大规模音频数据进行训练，只更新音频映射器的参数，使得模型具备对语音的理解和解释能力。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第三阶段</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是跨模态交互集成阶段。这一阶段基于前两阶段的模型参数，利用结合视觉和音频数据，提升模型处理和关联不同模态信息的能力。</span></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n   <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n     <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">02</span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n       <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">模型效果</span>\n      </section>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">情绪识别：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017462\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222222222223\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5bbeaf0-d8c3-43e0-5e2f-0eda305c1000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" title=\"\" width=\"1250\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5bbeaf0-d8c3-43e0-5e2f-0eda305c1000/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">面部表情描述：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017460\" data-ratio=\"0.7509259259259259\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4b1fdba0-6cee-4968-763f-e08864e24c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" title=\"\" width=\"919\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4b1fdba0-6cee-4968-763f-e08864e24c00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">动作理解：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017459\" data-ratio=\"0.6240740740740741\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a46a5bd1-a43a-4b11-ac29-0e05a87d5600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" title=\"\" width=\"844\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a46a5bd1-a43a-4b11-ac29-0e05a87d5600/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在这三个人物理解相关的任务上，我们的HumanOmni均达到了SOTA的水平。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ASR：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017458\" data-ratio=\"0.3472222222222222\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c43b80ff-574b-4324-bb4a-5031b01fbf00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" title=\"\" width=\"932\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c43b80ff-574b-4324-bb4a-5031b01fbf00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在ASR任务上，在Omni模型中，达到了先进的水平。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们也对模型中不同模态的作用进行了分析：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017463\" data-ratio=\"0.16203703703703703\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4144c4f8-f404-4e95-8e77-eb0bd779a900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" title=\"\" width=\"634\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4144c4f8-f404-4e95-8e77-eb0bd779a900/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该表格说明了HumanOmni理解了不同模态的信息，模型可以通过不同模态的信息来完成不同类型的任务。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n   <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n     <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">03</span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n       <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">模型推理</span>\n      </section>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们开源了推理代码，只需执行inference.py即可：<br></span></p>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"python\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">import os</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">import argparse</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">from humanomni import model_init, mm_infer</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">from humanomni.utils import disable_torch_init</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">from transformers import BertTokenizer</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">os.environ['TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE'] = '1'</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">os.environ['CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES'] = '0'</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">def main():</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"HumanOmni Inference Script\")</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    parser.add_argument('--modal', type=str, default='video_audio', help='Modal type (video or video_audio)')</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    parser.add_argument('--model_path', type=str, required=True, help='Path to the model')</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    parser.add_argument('--video_path', type=str, required=True, help='Path to the video file')</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    parser.add_argument('--instruct', type=str, required=True, help='Instruction for the model')</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    args = parser.parse_args()</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    # 初始化BERT分词器</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    bert_model = \"bert-base-uncased\"</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    bert_tokenizer = BertTokenizer.from_pretrained(bert_model)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    # 禁用Torch初始化</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    disable_torch_init()</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    # 初始化模型、处理器和分词器</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    model, processor, tokenizer = model_init(args.model_path)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    # 处理视频输入</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    video_tensor = processor['video'](args.video_path)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    # 根据modal类型决定是否处理音频</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    if args.modal == 'video_audio' or args.modal == 'audio':</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        audio = processor['audio'](args.video_path)[0]</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    else:</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">        audio = None</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    # 执行推理</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    output = mm_infer(video_tensor, args.instruct, model=model, tokenizer=tokenizer, modal=args.modal, question=args.instruct, bert_tokeni=bert_tokenizer, do_sample=False, audio=audio)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    print(output)</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">if __name__ == \"__main__\":</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    main()</span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">输入参数分别为</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">modal，控制使用的模态，这里可以选择video_audio（使用视觉+声音），video（仅使用视觉），audio（仅使用声音）。我们推荐同时使用视觉+声音。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">model_path，模型的路径。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">video_path，视频的路径。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">instruct，用户的指令。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\">我们的模型可以通过modelscope和huggingface进行获取。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n   <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n     <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">04</span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n       <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">模型微调</span>\n      </section>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们开放了模型微调的代码，供开发者使用我们的模型在数据集上进行微调。我们提供的方式是基于HumanOmni-Video（一阶段）和HumanOmni-Audio（二阶段）的参数，进行跨视觉和音频模态的微调。</span></p>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"properties\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">torchrun</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">--nnodes $WORLD_SIZE \\</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --nproc_per_node $NPROC_PER_NODE \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --master_addr=$MASTER_ADDR \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --master_port=$MASTER_PORT \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --node_rank $RANK \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    humanomni/train_flash_attn.py \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --deepspeed scripts/zero3.json \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --model_type HumanOmni_qwen2 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --model_path /mnt/data/jiaxing.zjx/code/HumanOmni/HumanOmni_7B_Video/ \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --vision_tower google/siglip-so400m-patch14-384 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --audio_tower openai/whisper-large-v3 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --mm_projector_type  all_in_one \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --mm_tunable_parts \"mm_mlp_adapter,audio_projector,mm_language_model\" \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --pretrain_audio_mlp_adapter /mnt/data/jiaxing.zjx/code/HumanOmni/HumanOmni_7B_Audio/audio_projector.bin \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --data_path   ./yamls/oryx_audio.yaml \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --data_folder / \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --mm_vision_select_layer -2 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --image_aspect_ratio pad \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --num_frames 32 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --bf16 True \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --tf32 True \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --fp16 False \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --output_dir ${OUTP_DIR}/${WANDB_PROJECT}/finetune_${RUN_NAME} \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --num_train_epochs 1 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --per_device_train_batch_size $LOCAL_BATCH_SIZE \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --per_device_eval_batch_size 4 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --gradient_accumulation_steps $GRADIENT_ACCUMULATION_STEPS \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --evaluation_strategy \"no\" \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --save_strategy \"steps\" \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --save_steps 500 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --save_total_limit 99 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --learning_rate 2e-5 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --weight_decay 0. \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --warmup_ratio 0.03 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --lr_scheduler_type \"cosine\" \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --logging_steps 1 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --model_max_length 2048 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --gradient_checkpointing True \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --mm_use_x_start_end True \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --dataloader_num_workers 4 \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --report_to tensorboard \\</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    --run_name $RUN_NAME \\</span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <pre data-language=\"plain\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></pre>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当然用户也可以基于我们最终的HumanOmni模型进行微调。取决于用户的数据量以及数据的相关程度。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n   <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n     <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">05</span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n       <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">效果展示</span>\n      </section>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们分别在电影片段、特写视频、实拍视频三个人物场景下测试了我们的模型的理解能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">电影片段：</span></p>\n  <section>\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3873142401166163968\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8ZLuyaibrZbkzM4mMoo13Gy0TjUv5lJeGFq9K9JuiaWnh7pibNMQAYENAD3mICKR4jkmicnboJeib8YkCblz1Husxicg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" data-w=\"1280\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3873142401166163968\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"sql\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">User:What's the major emotion?</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">HumanOmni:angry.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">User:What's the major facial expression?</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">HumanOmni:frown.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">User:Desribe the woman.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">HumanOmni:The woman has long brown hair and is wearing a pink top <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">with</span> a dark cardigan.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">User</span>:Please <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">describe</span> the major <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">action</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">in</span> detail.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">HumanOmni:The woman <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">is</span> frowning <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">and</span> shaking her <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">head</span>, indicating that she <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">is</span> angry. She <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">is</span> also gesturing <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">with</span> her hands <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">as</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">if</span> she <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">is</span> explaining something <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">or</span> emphasizing a point.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">User</span>:What did the woman say?</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">HumanOmni:The woman said <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Of course we object! I object, Steve!\"</span></span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <pre data-language=\"plain\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></pre>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">特写视频</span></p>\n  <section>\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3873143740877193231\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8ZLuyaibrZbkzM4mMoo13Gy0TjUv5lJeGVGIKN3ktmtyhH9RZ8oLErSs55uXYeuvpV9xUloR7uMibIzib2TlbG0bQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" data-w=\"1280\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3873143740877193231\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"css\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">User</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:What's</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">the</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">major</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">emotion</span>?</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">HumanOmni</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:happy.</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">User</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:What's</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">the</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">major</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">facial</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">expression</span>?</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">HumanOmni</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:smile.</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">User</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:Desribe</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">the</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">woman</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">in</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">detail</span>.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">HumanOmni</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:The</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">woman</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">in</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">the</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">video</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">has</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">blonde</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">hair</span>, <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">is</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">wearing</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">a</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">black</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">top</span>, <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">and</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">is</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">smiling</span>.</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">User</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:What</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">did</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">the</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">woman</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">say</span>?</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">HumanOmni</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-pseudo\">:The</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">woman</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">said</span> \"<span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">Dogs</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">are</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">sitting</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">by</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">the</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">door</span>.\"</span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <pre data-language=\"plain\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></pre>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实拍视频</span></p>\n  <section>\n   <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3873144542006149129\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8ZLuyaibrZbkzM4mMoo13Gy0TjUv5lJeGzI89QEus4tuADKgjicugUJZokqrMEkAkMWG3PqWGXmgs9dsj7G7JmZQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"0.5633802816901409\" data-w=\"320\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3873144542006149129\"></iframe>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"makefile\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__section\">User:描述一下视频中男子的外貌穿着.</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__section\">HumanOmni:视频中的男性有短的黑发，配戴圆框眼镜。他穿了一件棕色的毛大衣，内里是白色的.</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__section\">User:视频中男子说了什么内容？</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__section\">HumanOmni:男子说他穿什么颜色的衣服，现在处于什么环境，今天的天气怎么样.</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__section\">User:视频中男子有什么情绪吗？</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__section\">HumanOmni:没有情绪。</span></span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <pre data-language=\"plain\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></pre>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们在三类视频下，分别测试了模型对于主要依靠视觉内容进行回答的问题（外貌描述），主要依靠音频内容进行回答的问题（说话内容），依靠音视频共同回答的问题（情绪理解）的效果。我们的HumanOmni均有非常稳定且准确的输出。</span></p><article data-clipboard-cangjie=\"[&quot;root&quot;,{&quot;copyFrom&quot;:568702976},[&quot;h2&quot;,{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;m375v17nidk9zolvp1&quot;,&quot;spacing&quot;:{&quot;before&quot;:21.333333333333332,&quot;after&quot;:9,&quot;line&quot;:0.8529411764705882}},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;},[&quot;span&quot;,{&quot;sz&quot;:16,&quot;szUnit&quot;:&quot;pt&quot;,&quot;data-type&quot;:&quot;leaf&quot;},&quot;视频教程&quot;]]]]\" data-identifier-application__slash__x-cangjie-fragment=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"QvjnAAAeRzJynXo5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"QvjnAA9pBXJbnXo5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">\n       <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: center;\">\n        <mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe js_wx_tap_highlight\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-weuitheme=\"light\" data-id=\"MzkxNTM5NTg2OA==\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8ZLuyaibrZbkOjSAtkOUvy9rQ8dOrPJia7YibgOEuicFetibOyUhvyg32BibsId8ibIxpCVDowuFcZajFTqTRyTlPNqbg/300?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=19\" data-nickname=\"魔搭ModelScope社区\" data-alias=\"ModelScope\" data-signature=\"模型开源社区魔搭社区ModelScope官方账号\" data-from=\"2\" data-index=\"0\" data-origin_num=\"161\" data-isban=\"0\" data-biz_account_status=\"0\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\"></mp-common-profile><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"></span>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </article>\n   </article>\n  </article>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: block;color: var(--weui-FG-0);font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "HumanOmni 是首个专注于人类中心场景理解的多模态大模型，能够同时处理视觉和听觉信息，并在情绪识别等任务上达到 SOTA 水平。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "HumanOmni 是首个专注于人类中心场景理解的多模态大模型，能够同时处理视觉和听觉信息，并在情绪识别等任务上达到 SOTA 水平。",
  "summary": "HumanOmni 是业内首个专注于理解以人为中心的场景的多模态大模型，它能够同时处理视觉和音频信息。该模型通过结合视觉（面部、人体、环境）和听觉信息，并融入大语言模型，实现了对人类中心场景的更完整理解。其创新之处在于构建了大规模的人类中心视频数据集，并设计了针对人物场景的专用网络架构。实验结果表明，HumanOmni 在情绪识别、面部描述和动作理解等任务中均达到了当前最优水平，验证了视觉 + 音频联合输入的优势。此外，该文章还开源了推理和微调代码，为开发者提供了便利。HumanOmni 模型在人机交互、智能监控等领域具有实际应用潜力。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "HumanOmni 是首个专注于人类中心场景的多模态大模型",
      "explanation": "该模型能够同时处理视觉和音频信息，更全面地理解以人为中心的复杂场景。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大规模数据集和专用网络架构是模型成功的关键",
      "explanation": "通过构建包含 240 万视频片段的数据集，并设计针对人物场景的网络架构，提升了模型对人物中心场景的理解能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "音视频联合输入优于单一模态输入",
      "explanation": "实验证明，同时使用视觉和音频信息能够提高模型在情绪识别、动作理解等任务上的准确性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "HumanOmni 是业内首个理解以人为中心的场景，可以同时处理视觉信息、音频信息的多模态大模型。",
    "在情绪识别、面部描述、动作理解等多个人物相关的任务下，我们的 HumanOmni 均达到了 sota 的水平，同时我们实验验证了视觉 + 音频的联合输入相比单独使用视觉和单独使用音频的优势。",
    "我们的模型可以通过 modelscope 和 huggingface 进行获取。"
  ],
